    "The purpose of this approach is to try to give ChatGPT, in this way, a contextual example of similar symptoms of the disease, so that it can give a better description of the patient's symptoms.",
    "Similarly, in the \"Auxiliary examination\" part, \"generate the most relevant medical examination names, using {ls_aux_test} as an example\".",
    "The variable {ls_aux_ test} stores some medical examination names, such as \"complete blood count\", \"urinalysis\", \"stool routine\", \"chlamydia\", \"liver function\", \"kidney function\", etc.",
    "Eventually, ChatGPT is expected to give a better name for the auxiliary examinations performed by the patient based on the content of this variable {ls_aux_test}.",
    "For the rest of Fig. 9, some give specific examples, such as the \"Diagnosis\" part, and some give relevant explanations, such as the \"Present medical history\" part."
